methods.makeFillContext:
Allocate a new ChunkSource.FillContext for filling chunks from this FillContextMaker, typically a
 ChunkSource.

:param chunkCapacity: (int) - The maximum size of any WritableChunk that will be filled with this context
:param sharedContext: (io.deephaven.engine.v2.sources.chunk.SharedContext) - Shared store of intermediate results.
:return: (io.deephaven.engine.v2.sources.chunk.ChunkSource.FillContext) A context for use with fill operations
methods.mask:
This mask is applied to RowSequence which are passed into
 ChunkSource.getChunk(ChunkSource.GetContext, RowSequence) and
 ChunkSource.fillChunk(ChunkSource.FillContext, WritableChunk, RowSequence). This allows the PagingChunkSources to be cached, and reused even if they are properly relocated in key space.

:return: (long) the mask for this page, which must be a bitmask representing the some number of lower order bits of a
         long.
methods.parameters: :return: (io.deephaven.engine.v2.sources.regioned.RegionedPageStore.Parameters) The parameters object that describes this regioned page store
methods.regionMask:
:return: (long) The mask that should be applied to RowSequence indices when calculating their address within a
         region
methods.regionMaskNumBits: :return: (int) The number of bits masked by regionMask()
